{"tid":700642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「華山論劍」係咪中文歷史上最後出現既一個成語??????","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T05:36:01.000Z","uid":10338,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5c4c213e3667b7da854d8395895f4b846c41b7d3","tid":700642,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"應該係金庸創<br />\n開始有埋意思<br />\n算係近代??<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.18dao.net/%E6%88%90%E8%AA%9E%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%B8/%E8%8F%AF%E5%B1%B1%E8%AB%96%E5%8A%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.18dao.net%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%25AA%259E%25E8%25A9%259E%25E5%2585%25B8%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25AB%2596%25E5%258A%258D&d=E53vm%2Fe9zDsGBEJNBXY9RI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=60bc4e89\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.18dao.net/%E6%88%90%E8%AA%9E%E8%A9%9E%E5%85%B8/%E8%8F%AF%E5%B1%B1%E8%AB%96%E5%8A%8D</a><br />\n【釋義】：出自金庸的武俠小說《射雕英雄傳》，原意是華山比武，引申為公開的比試或學術爭鳴。含有以下含意：①比試各方都是高手；②公正較量，不耍陰謀。如：&ldquo;弈林高手六月華山論劍，四項比賽屆時同現西嶽&rdquo;&ldquo;因為，真正意義上的對手間的較量，絕不是無恥小人間的蠅營狗苟，絕不是無恥之徒間的暗中算計，而是青梅煮酒，是華山論劍，在切磋才學中相互提升著對方的品性和修養&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"1255e8d9f1ac3fd055510312141b418c859a38f0","tid":700642,"uid":25126,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:16:52.000Z","msg":"通商寬衣"},{"pid":"73fd07b02de9238e6a8827f3bf137df4567f0ff9","tid":700642,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:19:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/393777/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/393777/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"23cd19b1d2ffdc1c6405727c939fc370ef605fe0","tid":700642,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:20:28.000Z","msg":"十動然拒"},{"pid":"d1dd5939ec11af7e0ffd3aa453638b9aa62d5bbd","tid":700642,"uid":50060,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌"},{"pid":"46c8c111c1e65e8e514ecbbe45816f2741a47c5f","tid":700642,"uid":48066,"like":25,"d